îjntrnr 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/9907] re-aligned how prompt indicators work
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/9900] simplified default style and match Rust code to config
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/9893] reverted 9693 to prevent CPU hangs
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/9908] reverted "Add an option to move header on borders"
IanManske 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/9770] replaced 
``&Span``
 with 
``Span``
 since 
``Span``
 is 
``Copy``
fdncred 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/9905] removed 
``vectorize_over_list``
 from python plugin
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/9898] updated the 
``format``
 signature to allow 
``record``
 to be passed in
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/9896] updated the 
``items``
 signature to allow 
``any``
 output
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/9895] updated the 
``char``
 signature with 
``Table``
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/9877] updated to current reedline
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/9866] bumped to dev version 0.83.2
WindSoilder 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/9902] renamed 
``date format``
 to 
``format date``
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/9773] Module: support defining const and use const variables inside of function
ayax79 cleaned up some dataframe commands: 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/9860] merged overloaded commands
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/9858] merging into one 
``dfr into-nu``
 command
atahabaki created 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/9856] str-expand: add path flag
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/9841] str-expand: Add Escaping Example
ghost 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/9854] made URLs clickable in error documentation
mengsuenyan 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/9853] fixed a bug where 
``~ | path type``
 returned an empty string
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/9851] fixed a panic when type a statement similar to 
``let f = 'f' $``
 in the nushell
sholderbach 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/9814] updated 
``unicode-linebreak``
 to 
``0.1.5``
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/9788] added 
``format duration``
 to replace 
``into duration --convert``
zhiburt 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/9796] added an option to move header on borders
jflics6460 created 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/9771] Accept records for http subcommand headers (-H)
